### KHI focused album import — real folder data
### Albums: ڕەشۆڵ، تاهیر تۆفیق، مریەم خان، عەلی مەردان
### Source: /Users/khi/Downloads/Site/بابەتەکانی ئەپڵۆدکردن/Publish/Albums
### 4 album records; 209 media uploads; 4 preflights; 4 creates; 4 verification requests.
### Total: 222 requests including Login; approximately 2.41 GiB of media.
### Run Login first, then run one complete album at a time from top to bottom.
### Do not use parallel Run All. Do not rerun a successful Create request.
### If an upload returns HTTP 502 "upstream error", wait 20 seconds and rerun that same upload.
### Continue only after it returns HTTP 200; otherwise its URL variable will be missing at Create.
### Ali Mardan and Tahir Tofiq use their unique "All" tracks; byte-identical CD copies are skipped.

@baseUrl = https://blissful-spontaneity-production.up.railway.app
@username = akar
@password = 11111111

### Login
# @name login_missing_albums
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

> {%
  client.assert(response.status === 200, "Missing-albums login failed: HTTP " + response.status + " " + JSON.stringify(response.body));
  client.global.set("auth_token", response.body.token);
%}

